OL,3,CWhat are vertical farms and how can
OL,4,Cthey help with sustainable food
OL,5,Cproduction?
OL,7,FThe world's largest vertical farm has
OL,8,Fbeen set up in Gloucestershire.
OL,10,FThe Jones Food Company set up the farm
OL,11,Fcalled JFC2 in Lydney two years ago.
OL,13,FThe business grows a dozen different
OL,14,Ftypes of herbs and salad brands indoor
OL,15,Fin its Growing Room.
OL,17,FWhat is a vertical farm?
