OL,3,CWhat are vertical farms and how can
OL,4,Cthey help with sustainable food
OL,5,Cproduction?
OL,7,FVertical farming is the practice of
OL,8,Fgrowing crops in vertically stacked
OL,9,Flayers indoors rather than in
OL,10,Ftraditional horizontal fields.
OL,12,FAs the crops are grown in vertical
OL,13,Flayers, less land space is needed.
OL,15,FFor example, JFC2 has the equivalent
OL,16,Fof 70 tennis courts of growing space
OL,17,Fand the company's founder and CEO,
OL,18,FJames Lloyd-Jones, says it's an
OL,19,Fefficient process.
