OL,3,CWhat are vertical farms and how can
OL,4,Cthey help with sustainable food
OL,5,Cproduction?
OL,7,FHe said: "From an environmental
OL,8,Fperspective, vertical farming allows
OL,9,Fus to grow in 17 layers, so every acre
OL,10,Fbecomes 17 times more productive.
OL,12,F"It allows us to grow entirely without
OL,13,Fpesticides and using 95% less water.
OL,14,FAnd it means we can significantly
OL,15,Freduce the air and road miles of the
OL,16,Ffoods we grow.
OL,18,F"Our second farm is in Gloucestershire
OL,19,Fbecause it is well located for us in
OL,20,Fterms of distribution centres and
OL,21,Fcustomers.
