OL,3,CWhat are vertical farms and how can
OL,4,Cthey help with sustainable food
OL,5,Cproduction?
OL,7,F"There's a good motorway network,
OL,8,Fstrong labour candidate pool, and
OL,9,Fthere are established growers of a
OL,10,Fvariety of produce in that area so the
OL,11,Fskillset is established in the area
OL,12,Fwhich we can lean on."
OL,14,FHow do vertical farms work?
OL,16,FAs the crops are indoors, artificial
OL,17,Flighting and controlled environments
OL,18,Fare used to produce a high yield.
