OL,3,CWhat are vertical farms and how can
OL,4,Cthey help with sustainable food
OL,5,Cproduction?
OL,7,FIt means growth doesn't rely on the
OL,8,Fweather and can therefore be produced
OL,9,Fall year round rather than depending
OL,10,Fon the seasons.
OL,12,FOli Kaberry, Chief Operations Officer
OL,13,Fat Jones Food Company, said: "We can
OL,14,Fstack our acre vertically thereby
OL,15,Fmaximising the land efficiency.
OL,17,F"We use hydroponics as part of our
OL,18,Fmethodology which means we grow
OL,19,Fwithout soil but with a nutrient-rich
OL,20,Fsolution.
