OL,3,CWhat are vertical farms and how can
OL,4,Cthey help with sustainable food
OL,5,Cproduction?
OL,7,F"With the controlled environment
OL,8,Fagriculture that we've created, we
OL,9,Fhave been able to carve out a niche
OL,10,Fover the years making lab conditions
OL,11,Fin a huge warehouse space.
OL,13,F"That has enabled us to grow leafy
OL,14,Fgreens like green lettuces, mizuna,
OL,15,Fbulls blood, kale, and herbs like
OL,16,Fbasil, dill, coriander, parsley."
OL,18,FHow does it compare to traditional
OL,19,Ffarms?
