OL,3,CWhat are vertical farms and how can
OL,4,Cthey help with sustainable food
OL,5,Cproduction?
OL,7,FVertical farms can produce high yields
OL,8,Fall year round but operate with high
OL,9,Frunning costs.
OL,11,FThe costs come from controlling
OL,12,Flights, temperature, carbon dioxide
OL,13,Flevels, and water in the Growing Room.
OL,15,F"In terms of the efficiency of
OL,16,Fgrowing, this is really where vertical
OL,17,Ffarming comes into its own," he added.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/12
