OL,3,CWhat are vertical farms and how can
OL,4,Cthey help with sustainable food
OL,5,Cproduction?
OL,7,F"As an example we are able to grow
OL,8,Fgreen lettuce within 15 days whereas
OL,9,Foutdoor you may only have two or three
OL,10,Fgrowing cycles per year.
OL,12,F"We can have that replicability of
OL,13,Fthat harvest per annum to maximise our
OL,14,Fefficiency.
OL,16,F"Having those high yields justifies
OL,17,Fthe running costs that we are impacted
OL,18,Fby.
