OL,3,CWhat are vertical farms and how can
OL,4,Cthey help with sustainable food
OL,5,Cproduction?
OL,7,F"Overall we have higher costs than an
OL,8,Foutdoor grower but we're able to be
OL,9,Fprofitable by achieving those yields
OL,10,Fand that's what makes us able to keep
OL,11,Fthe lights on.
OL,13,F"The costs have heightened especially
OL,14,Fsince the 2022 energy spike and the
OL,15,Fprices we witnessed were pretty
OL,16,Fmonumental but we are working back
OL,17,Fdown to a better level which makes it
OL,18,Fa better model for us."
