OL,3,CWhat are vertical farms and how can
OL,4,Cthey help with sustainable food
OL,5,Cproduction?
OL,7,FVertical farms are discussed as a
OL,8,Fviable option for the future of food
OL,9,Fproduction given the commitment to use
OL,10,Frenewable energy.
OL,12,FAs climate change causes more extreme
OL,13,Fweather events, crop production can
OL,14,Fvary significantly on a yearly basis.
OL,16,FOli adds that he hopes vertical farms
OL,17,Fcan be scaled up in future to help
OL,18,Fpromote sustainable farming.
