OL,3,CWhat are vertical farms and how can
OL,4,Cthey help with sustainable food
OL,5,Cproduction?
OL,7,FHe says: "Our growing system is
OL,8,Fbasically focused on helping to work
OL,9,Fthrough the climate crisis and food
OL,10,Fshortages.
OL,12,F"We are using renewable energy to be
OL,13,Fas clean as possible and have little
OL,14,Fimpact on the environment.
OL,16,F"We also grow 365 days a year so we
OL,17,Fare consistently delivering to our
OL,18,Fcustomers so we are mitigating spikes
OL,19,Fcaused by the climate system.
